<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTPA10">
<l>ennā ḷemperu māṉuṉṟa ṉakkaṭi yōmeṉ ṟeḻuttuppaṭṭa</l>
<l>vannā ḷēyaṭi yōṅkaḷa ṭikkuṭil vīṭupeṟ ṟuyntatukāṇ</l>
<l>centāḷ tōṟṟit tirumatu raiyuṭcilai kuṉit taintalaiya</l>
<l>painnā kattalaip pāyntava ṉēyuṉṉaip pallāṇṭu kūṟutumē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Our Lord, the day on which we [became] your servants,</l>
<l rend="indent">that very day when the letter appeared,</l>
<l>we, who are your servants, obtained the salvation of freedom in the abode of [your] feet. See!</l>
<l>[On that] good day, we proclaim “many years” to you,</l>
<l rend="indent">the one who lept on the head of the five headed cobra,</l>
<l rend="indent">appearing in holy Maturai, roaring, and dancing.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
